item.title: CVE-2021-36319|2024-08-04T00:54:51.465Z -- dell -- dell%20networking%20os10
item.description: Dell Networking OS10 versions 10.4.3.x, 10.5.0.x and 10.5.1.x contain an information exposure vulnerability. A low privileged authenticated malicious user can gain access to SNMP authentication failure messages.

item.title: CVE-2021-36310|2024-08-04T00:54:51.446Z -- dell -- dell%20networking%20os10
item.description: Dell Networking OS10, versions 10.4.3.x, 10.5.0.x, 10.5.1.x & 10.5.2.x, contain an uncontrolled resource consumption flaw in its API service. A high-privileged API user may potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to a denial of service.
